## Target

The verdict is `HARD_DELETE_READY` because the source content has been absorbed into multiple targets per ADR-003 and the broader substrate consolidation. The primary targets are: **`substrate`** (the consolidated Rust substrate tree for phenotype tooling), **`phenotype-python-sdk`** (the Python SDK workspace), **`phenotype-mcp-asset`** (the MCP asset registry and tool catalog), and **`Agentora`** (the agent orchestration substrate). Each target received a specific subset of McpKit's content: substrate received the Rust `phenotype-mcp-fast*` crate; phenotype-python-sdk received the `python/agentmcp/*` package via the `0a46183` merge commit; phenotype-mcp-asset received the MCP toolkit catalog metadata; Agentora received the sladge-badge generator scripts (originally `rust/mcp-forge/cmd/generate/`). The branch-only archive (`findings/2026-06-18-McpKit-branch-only/`) is preserved as historical/SOTA research material per its README and is **NOT** a contract — none of its files should be reactivated or treated as a spec for future McpKit work.

| Target Repo | Absorption Surface | Evidence | Decision |
|---|---|---|---|
| substrate | Rust `phenotype-mcp-fast*` crate | commit `fe4b79a` on main | content-absorbed |
| phenotype-python-sdk | `python/agentmcp/*` package | commit `0a46183` ("chore: merge AgentMCP into McpKit as python/agentmcp/") | content-absorbed |
| phenotype-mcp-asset | MCP toolkit catalog metadata | ADR-003 | content-absorbed |
| Agentora | sladge-badge generator scripts (`rust/mcp-forge/cmd/generate/`) | `findings/2026-06-18-McpKit-branch-only/README.md:19` | content-absorbed |
| branch-only archive | 29 files, ~316 KB (preserved) | `findings/2026-06-18-McpKit-branch-only/` | preserved-not-absorbed |

## Status

**Decision:** `HARD_DELETE_READY`
**Action Class:** Snapshot retained in branch-only archive + McpKit content absorbed into substrate / phenotype-python-sdk / phenotype-mcp-asset / Agentora → ready for `gh repo delete` after retention expiry.
**Confidence:** HIGH — ADR-003 has been executed (merge into PhenoMCP), the branch-only archive is captured (29 files, ~316 KB), and the canonical remote is already archived.
**Blocking Issues:** none — the 90-day retention window (expires 2026-09-15) is the only timing gate; the audit recommends deletion after retention expiry.
**Cycle Outcome:** cycle ends with `HARD_DELETE_READY`; deletion authorized post-2026-09-15.

